{"tid":2226160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[割韭菜式備戰]中國軍方大量招聘技術文職　應徵者須交報名費　被嘲找炮灰不忘割韭","createTime":"2020-10-01T23:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T23:57:38.000Z","uid":204533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a4fe3a09f512ecf69e0d2b13d4a6a780159fd4","tid":2226160,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T23:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本周三（30日），中國軍方剛結束了近年來最大規模的技術類士官的招聘，引人關注的是，其中無人機、航海、航空航太、電子資訊、小語種等專業招收力度和招聘人數更是被空前加重。被認為市中國軍方備戰的意圖和重點方向十分明確。<br />\n<br />\n此外，中央軍委國防動員部、空軍、陸軍、西部戰區、以及聯勤保障部門近日連續發布公告，公開向社會招聘高達近萬名軍隊文職人員。根據招聘公告顯示，軍方此次招聘涵蓋了包括駕駛、炊事、通訊、電腦、文秘、管理幹部等多個工種，要求所有的應聘者必須具有大專或以上學歷。</blockquote><br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>儘管官方在有關招聘中宣稱是選拔軍隊所需要的人才，但在其招聘公告中，<span class=\"red\"><strong><strong>無一例外的要求每個報名者必須繳納50或100元的報名費。這也被坊間嘲笑即便是當炮灰，也要被割一把韭菜。</strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n對此，何先生指出，招聘、審核等這些原本應該屬於軍隊份內的基本成本，也被轉嫁到了應聘者自己頭上。但在中國，這只是常態。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/army-10012020074645.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Farmy-10012020074645.html&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=2a6e0b51\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/army-10012020074645.html</a>"},{"pid":"8652703d83d7455bf5d5745a4bd29c2ebdfe5790","tid":2226160,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T23:20:03.000Z","msg":"請炮灰都要報名費, 你係咪窮到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話中國對軍人, 烈士好好架咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0598390ad6cfdee275af345d439161a190c14f","tid":2226160,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T23:25:11.000Z","msg":"香港啲求職騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36e7f7bcd6e4771222c6e07e5d726c6818748f2","tid":2226160,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb0598390ad6cfdee275af345d439161a190c14f","tid":2226160,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T23:25:11.000Z","msg":"香港啲求職騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T23:54:20.000Z","msg":"仲衰過香港啲求職騙局<br />\n起碼人地唔會要你條命<br />\n入軍方做呢啲位, 比CCP推去前線死左都唔知咩事"},{"pid":"378bb436c5a39083acdd3e67fc13ce07f8c65b8a","tid":2226160,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e36e7f7bcd6e4771222c6e07e5d726c6818748f2","tid":2226160,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb0598390ad6cfdee275af345d439161a190c14f","tid":2226160,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T23:25:11.000Z","msg":"香港啲求職騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T23:54:20.000Z","msg":"仲衰過香港啲求職騙局<br />\n起碼人地唔會要你條命<br />\n入軍方做呢啲位, 比CCP推去前線死左都唔知咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T23:56:07.000Z","msg":"到時俾個鍵盤你上去打美軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a900c71491de1b22364b30f121104cfa1ec07a8","tid":2226160,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T23:57:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/breakup1984/status/1311586028810121216?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbreakup1984%2Fstatus%2F1311586028810121216%3Fs%3D21&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAmAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=c28d29dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbreakup1984%2Fstatus%2F1311586028810121216%3Fs%3D21&h=31806392\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/breakup1984/status/1311586028810121216?s=21</a>"}]}